  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258790/extras/c470d321af3fb069aa5a705ca6aed687.poster.avif?t=1731387605\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258790/extras/c470d321af3fb069aa5a705ca6aed687.webm?t=1731387605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258790/extras/c470d321af3fb069aa5a705ca6aed687.mp4?t=1731387605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Nothing to see here except a perfectly ordinary video store.</h2><br>Video Hole is an ongoing, episodic adventure game series revolving around a series of strange completely normal events that transpire in your local, intergalactic video store. In episode one, it’s business as usual as you navigate your soul-crushing job while solving mysteries and meeting new characters. Of course, things are never quite what they seem in the darkly mysterious world of cross-temporal, hard-format film rental.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a bright and colorful world around the only video store this side of the cosmos.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Interact with a unique cast of characters with over 1,000 lines of unique dialogue.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Uncover the mysteries of this mysterious business by completing tasks for mysterious strangers.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experience both an overt and ambient story by collecting items based on dialogue choices.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258790/extras/3aec8a1315fbcd0d48bfd768c318fb12.poster.avif?t=1731387605\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258790/extras/3aec8a1315fbcd0d48bfd768c318fb12.webm?t=1731387605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258790/extras/3aec8a1315fbcd0d48bfd768c318fb12.mp4?t=1731387605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
